=Premodern Chinese Philology (語文學） and Linguistics （語言學）=
==Sources==
===Theory of Language===
* [[正名|正名篇]]  by [[荀子]] (313-238BC)
===Lexicographical Works===
* [[爾雅]]  around 3rd century BC 
* [[小爾雅]]  compiled by 孔鮒 (lived appr. 264-208BCE)
* [[方言]] first century AD
* [[說文解字]] 
* [[釋名]]  compiled around 200 by 劉熙 or 劉珍
* [[廣雅]]  compiled by around 227-232
* [[玉篇]] compiled around 543 by [[顧野王]]
* [[篆隷萬象名義]]  Tenrei banshō myōgi, edited by Kūkai [[空海]] around 830-835
* [[大廣益會玉篇]] complied 1015 by [[陳彭年]]
* [[字彙]] by [[梅膺祚]] published in 1615; introduced system of 214 classifiers
* [[字彙補]]  published 1666
* [[康熙字典]]  published 1710
===Rhyme Books 韻書=== 
* [[切韻]] by [[陸法言]], 601 
* [[切韻]] by [[長孫訥言]], 677 
* [[刊謬缺切韻]] (corrected and supplemented) by [王仁煦]], 706
* [[唐韻]] first version published 706 by [[孫愐]]
* [[唐韻]] second version published 720 by [[孫愐]]
* [[切韻]] by [[李舟]], 763-84 
* [[廣韻]] (broad rhymes) compiled 1007-1008 by a team led by [[陳彭年]] and [[邱雍]]
* [[集韻]] (collected rhymes) by [[丁讀]], published 1037
* [[韻補]] by [[吳棫]] （1100-1154）, applied [[叶韻]]-method in a systematic way
* [[新刊韻略]] by [[王文鬱]], 1223, introduced [[平水韻]] (106 rhymes distributed among the four tones)
* [[中原音韻]]  compiled 1324
===Rhyme Tables 韻圖===
* [[韻鏡]] by 張麟之 prior to 1161
* [[七音略]] by [[鄭樵]] in [[通志]]
* [[四聲等字]], Southern Song 1127-1279
===Glosses on the Classics===
* [[經典釋文]]  by [[陸德明]], dated around 582-589
* [[一切經音義]] compiled 655 by [[玄應]]
* 慧琳音義 by [[慧琳]]
* 續一切經音義
* [[詩集傳]] by [[朱熹]], finished around 1186, applied [[叶韻]]-method in a unsystematic way as reading aid
* [[毛詩古音考]] (Investigation of the ancient rhymes of the Mao Shi) by [[陳第]]， published 1606 
===Grammar Explanations===
* [[文則]] by Chen Kui [[陳騤]],  1170
* [[語助]] by Lu Yiwei [[盧以緯]], preface 1324
* [[虛字說]] by [[袁仁林]]，finished 1710, published 1746
* [[助字辨略]] compiled by [[劉淇]]， preface dated 1711 （清康熙五十年）
* [[經傳釋詞]] compiled by [[王引之]]， preface dated 1798 （清嘉慶三年）
* [[馬氏文通]] by [[馬建忠]] and [[馬相伯]], preface dated 1898 （清光緒二十四年）
===Miscellaneous===
* [[干祿字書]]
* [[龍龕手鑑]]  completed 997
* [[字說]] by [[王安石]] (1021-1068)
* [[群經音辨]] by [[賈昌朝]] (998-1078)
* [[埤雅]]  edited by 陸佃 around 1078-1085
* [[蒙古字韻]]  14th century
* [[華夷譯語]] published 1389
* [[正字通]]  published 1627, supplement to 字彙
* [[音學五書]] by [[顧炎武]], published 1667, includes: 音論, 詩本音, 易音, 唐韻正, 古音表 
* [[戚林八音]]  compiled 17th century
* [[佩文韻府]]  1711

